### Sample Crawler

This is the code for crawling IMDB Top 250 page, and Individual Movie page.

It extracts the details of Top 250 movies, goes into each movie page,
and extracts the actor names.

### Run locally

- Install dependencies

```bash
pip3 install -r requirements.txt
```

- To get top movies

```bash
python3 getTopMovies.py
```

- To get actor names in movie Gran Torino

```bash
python3 getActorsInMovie.py
```

- To find top actors

```bash
python3 findTopActors.py
```
